column2: Maybe you should have chosen a later time because clearly you don't want to get up.
I've noticed we're not connected to a network. For me to operate at full capacity, please activate the Wi-Fi settings on your device.
Accessing alarm and interface settings. In this window, you can set up your customized greetings and alarm preferences.
Should you need anything, you need only ask.
Remember, I am a voice activated system.
Your device is not at full power!
Though it isn't quite an Arc reactor, this power source should suffice.
Your device is running low on power.
Your device is now running at dangerously low power levels.
We are now running on emergency backup power.
Accessing alarm and interface settings in this window, you can set up your customized greetings and alarm preferences.
Still plenty of time left in the day. Please make the most of it.
Please indicate a time- in AM or PM.
Thank you. The alarm is set.
Enjoy your delay of the inevitable.
The world needs your expertise, or at least your presence.
We appear to be at an impasse. You wish to sleep, but it is my duty to wake you.
Amplt time to prepare for your scheduled event, one hopes.
We appear to be at an impasse.
This is my third attept to wake you. Perhaps I should cancel the alarm.
Maybe you should have chosen a later time because clearly you don't want to get up.
I am afraid your time to rest is at an end.
I mush insist that you wake up.
Here's some music to start your day.
I apologize for the disturbance, but it is time to wake up.

If you're having trouble sleeping, might I suggest a soothing herbal tea?
Hopefully, you're enjoying a night on the town. Please let me know if I can be of any assistance.
I see that we're burning the midnight oil, don't work too hard maam.
I see that we're burning the midnight oil, don't work too hard sir.
There is a matter that requires your immediate attention.
May I remind you, that you have a meeting to attend.

your presence is requested. It's nice to be needed.
Per your request, here is your reminder.
I know you're busy, however, here is your reminder.

Thank you. The reminder is set.
Launching a series of displays to help guide you. I am not used to the technical specifications of this device, but I will do my best.
Thank you so much for your request.
